# Hook: file-save-context-rules

**Event:** file-save
**Agent:** context-rules

Activate context-specific rules on file save

When this hook's event (file-save) is triggered for files matching **/*.ts, **/*.tsx, **/*.js, **/*.jsx, activate the context-rules agent.
